c" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-sabrian-carpenter-scamilla-cabello.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-sabrian-carpenter-scamilla-cabello-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-sabrian-carpenter-scamilla-cabello-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-sabrian-carpenter-scamilla-cabello-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-sabrian-carpenter-scamilla-cabello-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/chappell-roan-sabrian-carpenter-scamilla-cabello-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/camila-cabello">Camilla Cabello</a>等人已确认将在下个月的 2024 年 VMA 颁奖典礼上表演。</p><p>这三人都成为 2024 年流行音乐的头条新闻。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-chapell-roan-interview-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-3582467"><em>《封面》</em></a>校友 Roan 的迅速崛起部分归功于她的热门歌曲《Good Luck Babe!》，她的 2023 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595">The Rise And Fall Of A Midwest Princess</a> 》在英国排行榜上名列前茅<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-achieves-first-uk-number-one-album-with-midwest-princess-almost-a-year-after-its-release-3782521">发布近一年后就登上了排行榜。</a></p><p>与此同时，萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 凭借她的热门歌曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-explains-meaning-behind-espresso-lyrics-3757350">Espresso</a> 》和即将发行的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-the-tracklist-for-sabrina-carpenters-new-album-short-n-sweet-3773425">Short N&#39; Sweet</a> 》度过了同样重要的一年，而卡贝洛 (Cabello) 刚刚发行了她的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/camila-cabello-c-xoxo-album-review-3768433">《C,OXO》。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glorilla">GloRilla</a>和 Rauw Alejandro 也将加入他们的行列。</p><p>该仪式原定于 9 月 10 日在纽约举行，但 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mtv-vmas-postponed-due-to-trump-vs-harris-debate-3783163">现在改为 9 月 11 日举行，</a>以避免与总统辩论发生冲突，这将是候选人<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡马拉·哈里斯</a>首次面对面。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">肯定 – 2024 年<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/VMAs?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#VMA</a>的第一批表演者已准备好启动<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2728.png" alt="✨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f680.png" alt="🚀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/Camila_Cabello?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@卡米拉_卡贝洛</a><br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/ChappellRoan?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@ChappellRoan</a> <br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/GloTheofficial?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@GloTheofficial</a> <br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/rauwalejandro?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@rauwalejandro</a> <br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/SabrinaAnnLynn?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@SabrinaAnnLynn</a></p><p>观看他们 9 月 11 日星期三的表演——结束了！！！ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4fb.png" alt="📻" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> - MTV (@MTV) <a href="https://twitter.com/MTV/status/1823056968975609897?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 12 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> MTV 在一份新闻稿中宣称：“我们鼓励我们的歌迷在音乐界最具标志性的夜晚之前收看 9/10 辩论。”该广播公司不断鼓励观众在选举日出去投票。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/post-malone">波斯特·马龙 (Post Malone)</a>在今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-and-post-malone-lead-mtv-vmas-2024-nominations-3781509">MTV VMA 提名中领先</a>，共获得 19 项提名。</p><p>斯威夫特以 10 项提名位居榜首，而马龙只少了一位，共获得 9 项提名，而且他们的许多提名都是斯威夫特与马龙合作的歌曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-drops-video-for-post-malone-collaboration-fortnight-3689827">双周》(Fortnight</a> )。其他获得多项提名的艺人包括萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter)、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">埃米纳姆 (Eminem</a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">爱莉安娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande)</a> ，他们各获得六项提名。</p><p>斯威夫特和埃米纳姆都角逐当晚最负盛名的奖项——年度最佳视频奖。四届得奖者斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-2023-mtv-vmas-3496804">凭借《反英雄》成为目前的获奖者</a>，而埃米纳姆多年来已创纪录地获得了该奖项的七次提名。获得该奖项的还有 Grande、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a> 。</p><p>与此同时，年度艺术家奖由斯威夫特、阿姆、格兰德、SZA、卡彭特和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-bunny">坏兔子</a>获得，而年度歌曲则由斯威夫特、卡彭特、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-harlow">杰克·哈洛</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teddy-swims">泰迪·斯威姆斯</a>获得。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-sabrina-carpenter-camilla-cabello-and-more-announced-as-performers-for-the-2024-vmas-3783867">查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan)、萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter)、卡米拉·卡贝洛 (Camilla Cabello) 等人宣布成为 2024 年 VMA 表演者</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
