om/artists/renee-rapp">Reneé Rapp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pendulum">Pendulum</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kenny-beats">Kenny Beats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beadbadoobee">Beabadoobee</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kenya-grace">Kenya Grace</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">Nia Archives</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/two-door-cinema-club">Two Door Cinema Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Neck-Deep">Neck Deep</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wombats">The Wombats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Ashnikko">Ashnikko</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">Rachel Cinouriri</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 。</p><p>今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2023-line-up-headliners-announced-tickets-3363511">2024 年的头条新闻已公布，</a>其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/LIAM-GALLAGHER">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BLINK-182">Blink-182</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/FRED-AGAIN">Fred Again..</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gerry-cinnamon">Gerry Cinnamon</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/21-savage">21 Savage</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jorja-smith">Jorja Smith</a> （在英国音乐节独家演出）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-prodigy">The Prodigy</a>也于 11 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/reading/21-savage-jorja-smith-and-the-prodigy-added-to-reading-and-leeds-2024-line-up-3550922">宣布加入该法案</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beabadoobee-really-nervous-but-excited-for-reading-leeds-2024-3783857">Beabadoobee 的帖子“真的很紧张”，但对 Reading &amp; Leeds 2024 感到兴奋，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>