p>在新闻稿中谈到帮助创作这张唱片的主题和经历时，这位歌手分享道：“在圣经的后半部分，耶稣问‘人若赚得全世界，赔上自己的灵魂，有什么益处呢？ &#39;最近我发现以不同的方式提问很有趣。 “如果一个人失去了整个世界，却夺回了自己的灵魂，那对他有什么好处呢？”我认为答案一定是——天国。” </p><figure id="attachment_3783851" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3783851" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3783851" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Christopher-Owens-I-Wanna-Run-Barefoot-Through-Your-Hair-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS.jpg" alt="克里斯托弗·欧文斯《我想赤脚穿过你的头发》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Christopher-Owens-I-Wanna-Run-Barefoot-Through-Your-Hair-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Christopher-Owens-I-Wanna-Run-Barefoot-Through-Your-Hair-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Christopher-Owens-I-Wanna-Run-Barefoot-Through-Your-Hair-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Christopher-Owens-I-Wanna-Run-Barefoot-Through-Your-Hair-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Christopher-Owens-I-Wanna-Run-Barefoot-Through-Your-Hair-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Christopher-Owens-I-Wanna-Run-Barefoot-Through-Your-Hair-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Christopher-Owens-I-Wanna-Run-Barefoot-Through-Your-Hair-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3783851" class="wp-caption-text">克里斯托弗·欧文斯《我想赤脚穿过你的头发》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><strong>“我想赤脚穿过你的头发”曲目列表是</strong></p><p><strong>1.“不好”</strong><br /> <strong>2.《美丽的马》</strong><br /> <strong>3.“我想到天堂”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“白旗”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“我知道”</strong><br /> <strong>